o over half a million homebuyers and sellers monthly. Learn more at BrightMLS.com.###CONTACT: Christy ReapBright MLS2023099362christy.reap@brightmls.com	ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS	https://www.manilatimes.net/2025/04/10/tmt-newswire/globenewswire/bright-mls-march-2025-housing-report-the-spring-housing-market-ramps-up-in-the-mid-atlantic/2090342	https://www.manilatimes.net/manilatimes/uploads/images/2025/04/10/591719.jpg	2025-04-10 14:30:11
